summary: a blurb about sucking h’s fingers after he’s been too rough at sex? UGH MY MIND
question: a blurb about sucking h’s fingers after he’s been too rough at sex? UGH MY MIND
answer:
Well fuck.

He was rough. Too rough for you not to be able to walk tomorrow morning, he rarely became that needy in your relationship, but you didn’t bother to say anything. You haven’t seen each other for a whole 6 months, and that’s an acceptable reason for him to be an animal in bed.

Both of you out of breath as he laid down beside you, he turned over his side and just stared at you for a moment. He fucked you up real good, and he’s proud of that, your messy and sweaty forehead in display is enough for him to be hard again, he is so ready for another round, but your feelings is the main priority for him.

“You okay?” His soft voice said. He placed his hand on your thighs but quickly pulling away when you winced in pain, he just ran his hand through your hair, trying his best to calm you down.

“I literally came 3 times in one night, Harry.” You groaned pressing your cheeks harder on the pillow making him smirk to himself.

“I’m sorry, petal. I just missed you so much.” He pressed a long kiss on your forehead, you gave him a smile and kissed his palm on your cheeks. You took a deep breathe as his thumb ran over your cheeks and on your bottom lip.

“S’okay.” You gave him a reassuring smile.

“Open them fo’ me.” He whispered, bringing his thumb on your lips. He knows that it’s one of things that can calm you down, even though it’s hard to remember every little detail, it was an advantage for him. The way you closed your eyes, swirling your lips around his thumb is an amazing view for him.

You pulled away making a small pop sound, and smiled at him. He was about to say ‘good night’ but a thought came into your head.

“I could give you a bl—“ He cut you off by pulling you closer and just ran his fingers along your spine.

“You need rest, babe. Don’t worry about me, I already feel great by just being inside of you.”

It’s actually currently 4:51am here in Canada and the pain woke me up 🙄 & I am absolutely fine with all the fluff!!!! Maybe he’s helping with the physio exercise or something? whatever you write will be amazing regardless!! AGHH I LOVE U TOO XOXO

summary: How do you think Harry would feel about his girlfriend smoking? I smoke weed because it helps my anxiety and I can only get a...
question: How do you think Harry would feel about his girlfriend smoking? I smoke weed because it helps my anxiety and I can only get a full nights sleep if I smoke before going to bed, do you think he’d understand if that was the case?
answer: I think he’d totally support it! Honestly, I think Harry himself has smoked and he’d probably do anything he could to show her that he understands. He wouldn’t judge and would maybe even smoke with her if she was feeling more anxious than usual- if there were something she was nervous about or something she couldn’t handle on her own, it would probably be a big gesture to him to do it with her to silently reassure her that she wasn’t on her own. I think it might be a different case with cigarettes because it’s hurting her but instead of getting angry with her or pushing her to quit, he’d slowly ween her off of it by distracting her when she felt that itch. Idk, Harry just comes off as being very supportive of his s/o’s lifestyle and, if he really liked them, I don’t think he’d make a big deal about it unless it was positive.
